oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Interior of the Star Barber Shop
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Interior of the Star Barber Shop on South Spring Street. Charlie Lowry was the barber on the right and Wade West, the owner, is on the left.
A beauty shop is in this location now.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Barbershops; Barbers; Interiors
